data.description:
*** Price Improvement!**** Schedule your showing!!

Step into this beautiful  ranch home just waiting for someone to move in! You will fall in love with the open feel of this home! It has 2 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and an office right off of the living room! Gourmet kitchen with a double oven! Unwind after a long day or enjoy coffee in the morning in the cozy sunroom! There is also a shed and 2 attic entrances for extra storage. Custom built cabinets and workshop in the garage. This home was originally a model home and has been well maintained! Located in the desirable community of Walnut Creek with ammenities galore- 2 community pools, fitness center, clubhouse, walking trails and tennis courts! There is so much to do here!
Don't wait schedule an appointment to view this home! The holidays are right around the corner!
